Of Philip it's ſaid, not onely that he evangelized, but it's alſo ſaid of him, that he preached Chriſt to them of Samaria; 

                  〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉
               , Acts 8.5. and he baptized them alſo, verſ. 12; which is not ſaid of any of the other Diſciples which were of this diſperſion, either in the eighth or eleventh Chapter.

Secondly, The Diſciples in Acts 11.19, 20, 'tis ſaid, They ſpake the word to none but to the Jews onely; 
